<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="821" height="520" viewBox="0 0 821 520"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="white"/><g class="sequence-participant puml-node" data-participant="A" data-puml-id="A" data-puml-kind="participant" data-puml-family="sequence" data-puml-bbox="24.0 24.0 120.0 32.0"><rect x="24" y="24" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="84" y="45" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="A" data-puml-label-kind="participant-label" data-puml-bbox="80.0 32.8 8.1 17.0" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">A</text></g><g class="sequence-participant puml-node" data-participant="B" data-puml-id="B" data-puml-kind="participant" data-puml-family="sequence" data-puml-bbox="184.0 24.0 120.0 32.0"><rect x="184" y="24" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="244" y="45" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="B" data-puml-label-kind="participant-label" data-puml-bbox="240.0 32.8 8.1 17.0" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">B</text></g><line class="sequence-lifeline puml-edge" data-participant="A" data-puml-edge-id="lifeline:A" data-puml-family="sequence" data-puml-edge-kind="lifeline" data-puml-from="A" data-puml-to="A" x1="84" y1="56" x2="84" y2="464" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><line class="sequence-lifeline puml-edge" data-participant="B" data-puml-edge-id="lifeline:B" data-puml-family="sequence" data-puml-edge-kind="lifeline" data-puml-from="B" data-puml-to="B" x1="244" y1="56" x2="244" y2="464" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><rect x="24" y="200" width="730" height="72" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#eef6ff" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><polygon points="24,200 56,200 56,214 50,220 24,220" fill="#eef6ff" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="30" y="214" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="group:ref" data-puml-label-kind="group-header" data-puml-bbox="30.0 203.2 20.5 15.0" font-family="monospace" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#111">ref</text><text x="32" y="232" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="group:ref" data-puml-label-kind="group-label" data-puml-bbox="32.0 220.5 67.0 16.0" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">over A, B</text><text x="32" y="248" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="group:ref" data-puml-label-kind="group-label" data-puml-bbox="32.0 236.5 758.9 16.0" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">External dependency handshake with a very long descriptive line that previously escaped the ref block.</text><text x="32" y="264" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="group:ref" data-puml-label-kind="group-label" data-puml-bbox="32.0 252.5 639.8 16.0" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">Return payload includes another long descriptive line to stress multiline measurement.</text><rect x="24" y="320" width="751" height="120" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><polygon points="24,320 771,320 771,334 765,340 24,340" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="32" y="334" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="group" data-puml-label-kind="group-header" data-puml-bbox="32.0 322.5 781.2 16.0" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="#111">group This group label is intentionally verbose so the container width follows measured content correctly</text><line x1="84" y1="80" x2="244" y2="80" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="244,80 236,75 236,85" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><line class="puml-edge" data-sequence-from="A" data-sequence-to="B" data-puml-edge-id="message:A:B:80" data-puml-family="sequence" data-puml-edge-kind="message" data-puml-from="A" data-puml-to="B" x1="84" y1="80" x2="244" y2="80" stroke="none" pointer-events="none"/><text x="92" y="72" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="message:A:B:80" data-puml-label-kind="message-label" data-puml-bbox="92.0 60.5 52.1 16.0" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">kickoff</text><line x1="84" y1="360" x2="244" y2="360" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="244,360 236,355 236,365" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><line class="puml-edge" data-sequence-from="A" data-sequence-to="B" data-puml-edge-id="message:A:B:360" data-puml-family="sequence" data-puml-edge-kind="message" data-puml-from="A" data-puml-to="B" x1="84" y1="360" x2="244" y2="360" stroke="none" pointer-events="none"/><text x="92" y="352" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="message:A:B:360" data-puml-label-kind="message-label" data-puml-bbox="92.0 340.5 29.8 16.0" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">work</text><path class="sequence-note puml-node" data-puml-id="note:0:A, B" data-puml-kind="note" data-puml-family="sequence" data-puml-bbox="24.0 120.0 703.0 48.0" d="M24,120 H713 L727 134 V168 H24 Z" fill="#fff8c4" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M713 120 V134 H727" fill="none" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="32" y="140" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="note:0:A, B" data-puml-label-kind="note-label" data-puml-bbox="32.0 128.5 721.7 16.0" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">This is a very long yellow note line that should force the container to grow wider than defaults.</text><text x="32" y="156" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="note:0:A, B" data-puml-label-kind="note-label" data-puml-bbox="32.0 144.5 498.5 16.0" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">And this second line keeps the multiline height constraints honest.</text><g class="sequence-participant puml-node" data-participant="A" data-puml-id="A" data-puml-kind="participant" data-puml-family="sequence" data-puml-bbox="24.0 464.0 120.0 32.0"><rect x="24" y="464" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="84" y="485" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="A" data-puml-label-kind="participant-label" data-puml-bbox="80.0 472.8 8.1 17.0" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">A</text></g><g class="sequence-participant puml-node" data-participant="B" data-puml-id="B" data-puml-kind="participant" data-puml-family="sequence" data-puml-bbox="184.0 464.0 120.0 32.0"><rect x="184" y="464" width="120" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="244" y="485" class="puml-label" data-puml-owner="B" data-puml-label-kind="participant-label" data-puml-bbox="240.0 472.8 8.1 17.0" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">B</text></g></svg>
